### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "password": "12345",
  "email": "demo_user@gmail.com",
  "phone": "0900000000"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "user1",
  "password": "12345"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout

### Me (requires session cookie from login)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/account/me

### Update profile (requires session cookie from login)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/account/me
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1+updated@gmail.com",
  "phone": "0999999999"
}
